{"tid":605042,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"<學護溝藥參考> 內科常見藥","createTime":"2018-03-25T09:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T01:29:03.000Z","uid":91411,"like":27,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a096fb902e5dfb2b3aa788b69548da32b79d16b3","tid":605042,"uid":91411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:45:42.000Z","msg":"小弟以前做護士學生<br />\n一直都唔係好知某D 藥點溝<br />\n呢個post 主要分享下我做果度常用既藥同埋點溝<br />\n當然間間醫院可能都有d 唔同，post只作參考<br />\n等大家有個知字<br />\n<br />\nWFI:water for injection, NS:normal saline<br />\nantibiotics 篇：<br />\nAugmentin 1.2G : 用20ml WFI 開<br />\nTazocin 4.5G: 可用20ml WFI 開 bolus 打<br />\n                         可抽溝落100ml NS infusion<br />\n                         (by simple drip set)<br />\nampicillin: 10ml WFI <br />\ncloxacillin: 10ml WFI <br />\nzinacef: 10ml WFI <br />\nsulperazon： 1g 就10ml WFI, 2g 就20ml <br />\nmeropenem: 20ml WFI bolus or <br />\n                       可抽溝落100ml NS infusion<br />\n                         (by simple drip set)<br />\nVancomycin: 500mg 就100ml NS infusion <br />\n                        1000mg 就 250 ml NS infusion <br />\n                         at least one hour / no bolus<br />\n                         infusion machine needed<br />\n<br />\n其他藥物篇：<br />\nhydrocortisone: 5ml WFI <br />\npantoloc: 10ml NS for bolus or<br />\n                  100ml NS for infusion (by machine)<br />\ntransamine: 不用溝<br />\nvit k1: 不用溝<br />\ntramadol： 不用溝<br />\nnexium: 100ml NS for infusion (by machine)<br />\ndopamine 200mg : 100ml NS for infusion (by <br />\n                                   machine)<br />\namiordarone: loading lose  150mg in 100ml D5(by machine), maintenance dose 600mg in 500ml D5<br />\nlabetalolo: D5 for infusion ( 要岩prescribed concentration ？mg/ml ) by machine<br />\nDI  drip: actrapid + D50  (by infusion pump)<br />\nInsulin pump: actrapid + NS (by infusion pump)<br />\nSodium bicarbonate: prepared , infusion by machine <br />\nFlagyl: prepared. Infusion by machine<br />\nCalcium gluconate: bolus(slow inject), usually by doctor<br />\nDilantin: bolus (slow inject)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時咁多，稔唔到住，有可留言問。討論下"},{"pid":"3770e81def63468ff831057f2cfceb9f2b37515f","tid":605042,"uid":91411,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a096fb902e5dfb2b3aa788b69548da32b79d16b3","tid":605042,"uid":91411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:45:42.000Z","msg":"小弟以前做護士學生<br />\n一直都唔係好知某D 藥點溝<br />\n呢個post 主要分享下我做果度常用既藥同埋點溝<br />\n當然間間醫院可能都有d 唔同，post只作參考<br />\n等大家有個知字<br />\n<br />\nWFI:water for injection, NS:normal saline<br />\nantibiotics 篇：<br />\nAugmentin 1.2G : 用20ml WFI 開<br />\nTazocin 4.5G: 可用20ml WFI 開 bolus 打<br />\n                         可抽溝落100ml NS infusion<br />\n                         (by simple drip set)<br />\nampicillin: 10ml WFI <br />\ncloxacillin: 10ml WFI <br />\nzinacef: 10ml WFI <br />\nsulperazon： 1g 就10ml WFI, 2g 就20ml <br />\nmeropenem: 20ml WFI bolus or <br />\n                       可抽溝落100ml NS infusion<br />\n                         (by simple drip set)<br />\nVancomycin: 500mg 就100ml NS infusion <br />\n                        1000mg 就 250 ml NS infusion <br />\n                         at least one hour / no bolus<br />\n                         infusion machine needed<br />\n<br />\n其他藥物篇：<br />\nhydrocortisone: 5ml WFI <br />\npantoloc: 10ml NS for bolus or<br />\n                  100ml NS for infusion (by machine)<br />\ntransamine: 不用溝<br />\nvit k1: 不用溝<br />\ntramadol： 不用溝<br />\nnexium: 100ml NS for infusion (by machine)<br />\ndopamine 200mg : 100ml NS for infusion (by <br />\n                                   machine)<br />\namiordarone: loading lose  150mg in 100ml D5(by machine), maintenance dose 600mg in 500ml D5<br />\nlabetalolo: D5 for infusion ( 要岩prescribed concentration ？mg/ml ) by machine<br />\nDI  drip: actrapid + D50  (by infusion pump)<br />\nInsulin pump: actrapid + NS (by infusion pump)<br />\nSodium bicarbonate: prepared , infusion by machine <br 